Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Cagangohan Elementary School in the Municipality of Panabo, Province of Davao, to Dondoy Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 852
An Act Changing the Name of the Cagangohan Elementary School in the Municipality of Panabo, Province of Davao, to Dondoy Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Cagangohan Elementary School in the Municipality of Panabo, Province of Davao, is changed to Dondoy Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
